'''大川隆法'''（{{lang-ja|おおかわ りゅうほう}}，{{bd|1956年|7月7日|||catIdx=Okawa Ryuho}}），原名'''中川隆'''（{{lang-ja|なかがわ たかし}}）<ref name="unseenjapan">{{cite web | url=https://unseenjapan.com/happy-science/ | title=Inside "Happy Science", Japan's Far-Right Religious Movement | work=Unseen Japan | date=2019-08-12 | accessdate=2020-04-20 | author=Oskow, Noah}}</ref>，是日本[[新興宗教|新興宗教]]團體[[幸福科學|幸福科學]]創始人及總裁，自称[[释迦摩尼|释迦摩尼]][[转世|转世]]{{sfn|塚田穂高|2015|pp=295-296}}。

他在1986年創立「幸福科學」，之後又成立了New Star Production和ARI Production兩家藝能經紀公司<ref name="profile">{{cite web|url= https://ryuho-okawa.org|script-title= ja:大川隆法ご紹介|trans-title= Profile of Ryuho Okawa|work= Happy Science|publisher= IRH Press|location= Japan|language= ja|access-date= 2021-03-27|archive-date= 2021-05-27|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210527103615/https://ryuho-okawa.org/|dead-url= no}}</ref>以及[[幸福實現黨|幸福實現黨]]。他的宗教經常被批評為[[邪教|邪教]]<ref name=Musasizi>{{cite news |url=http://www.observer.ug/component/content/article?id=19408:clerics-call-for-probe-into-happy-science |title=Clerics call for probe into Happy Science |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222092033/http://www.observer.ug/component/content/article?id=19408:clerics-call-for-probe-into-happy-science |archivedate=2015-12-22 |last=Musasizi |first=Simon |newspaper=[[The_Observer_(Uganda)|The Observer]] |date=2012-06-21 |url-status=yes |accessdate=2021-03-27 }}</ref><ref name=thejakartapost>{{cite news |url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2012/07/22/happy-science-a-new-cult-offers-celebrity-guide-heaven.html |title=Happy Science, a new cult offers celebrity guide to heaven |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120825072332/http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2012/07/22/happy-science-a-new-cult-offers-celebrity-guide-heaven.html |newspaper=[[The_Jakarta_Post|The Jakarta Post]] |date=2012-07-22 |archivedate=2012-08-25 |accessdate=2021-03-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Donnelly>{{cite news |url=http://www.theage.com.au/victoria/blooming--happy-science-cult-channels-disney-ghandi-jesus-and-thatcher-20151028-gkkzow.html |title=Blooming 'Happy Science' religion channels Disney, Gandhi, Jesus and Thatcher |last=Donnelly |first=Beau |newspaper=[[The_Age|The Age]] |date=2015-11-02 |access-date=2017-11-25 |archive-date=2015-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151205191100/http://www.theage.com.au/victoria/blooming--happy-science-cult-channels-disney-ghandi-jesus-and-thatcher-20151028-gkkzow.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==簡介==
[[file:Ryuho_Okawa_2009.jpg|left]]
中川隆從[[東京大學|東京大學]]畢業後，在一家貿易公司工作，其後被派遣到[[美國|美國]][[紐約|紐約]]時，在[[紐約城市大學|紐約城市大學]]修讀國際金融學。1986年，他辭職創立幸福科學。

根據官方說法，大川隆法寫了超過2000本書<ref name="jt20090804" />，但實際上這些都只是他演講的文字版<ref name="Saint-Guily">{{cite magazine|url=https://www.vice.com/read/my-afternoon-with-a-failed-japanese-cult|title=Happy Science Is the Laziest Cult Ever|last=Saint-Guily|first=Sylla|date=3 October 2012|magazine=[[Vice_(magazine)|Vice]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151127162701/https://www.vice.com/read/my-afternoon-with-a-failed-japanese-cult|archivedate=2015-11-27|access-date=2021-03-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他又製作過19部電影<ref name="profile"/>。

1988年，大川隆法與木村恭子結婚，她其後擔任幸福實現黨總裁<ref name="jt20090804">{{Citation|last = McNeill|first = David|title = Party offers a third way: happiness|newspaper = [[The_Japan_Times|The Japan Times]]|date = 2009-08-04|url = http://www.japantimes.co.jp/community/2009/08/04/issues/party-offers-a-third-way-happiness|accessdate = 2009-08-06|archive-date = 2021-03-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210320040848/https://www.japantimes.co.jp/community/2009/08/04/issues/party-offers-a-third-way-happiness/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。但兩人已於2012年離婚<ref>''Shūkan Bunshun'' 3 February 2011, p. 140–43</ref><ref>''Shūkan Shinchō'' 3 February 2011, pp.136–37</ref>。其後幸福科學宣布她因對該組織造成傷害，在各大報章上誹謗該組織以及污辱愛爾康大靈等而被永久開除。 <ref name="liberty20110222">{{cite web|url= http://www.the-liberty.com/article.php?item_id=1385|script-title= ja:幸福の科学が大川きょう子氏を永久追放|trans-title= Happy Science permanently expels Kyoko Okawa|first= |last= |author= |authorlink= |date= 2011-02-22|work= The Liberty Web|publisher= IRH Press Co., Ltd.|location= |language= ja|accessdate= 2012-07-02|archive-date= 2020-08-09|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200809061439/https://the-liberty.com/article.php?item_id=1385|dead-url= no}}</ref>之後他又於2012年與教團職員近藤紫央結婚<ref>{{Cite book|title=In Love with the Sun: Spiritual Messages from Goddess Gaia|last=Okawa|first=Ryuho Okawa & Shio|date=2014-11-21|publisher=IRH Press Company Limited|isbn=9781941779262|language=en}}</ref>。

大川曾經被[[奧姆真理教|奧姆真理教]]於1995年1月企圖用[[VX神經毒劑|VX神經毒劑]]暗殺<ref>[[Richard_Danzig|Danzig, Richard]], [[Marc_Sageman|Marc Sageman]], Terrance Leighton, Lloyd Hough, Hidemi Yuki, Rui Kotani and Zachary M. Hosford, "[http://www.cnas.org/files/documents/publications/CNAS_AumShinrikyo_Danzig_1.pdf Aum Shinrikyo: Insights Into How Terrorists Develop Biological and Chemical Weapons] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnas.org/files/documents/publications/CNAS_AumShinrikyo_Danzig_1.pdf |date=20120324102229 }}", ''[[Center_for_a_New_American_Security|Center for a New American Security]]'', July 2011.</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Astley|first=Trevor|date=1995|title=The Transformation of a Recent Japanese New Religion: Ōkawa Ryūhō and Kōfuku no Kagaku|url=https://www.jstor.org/stable/30234459|journal=Japanese Journal of Religious Studies|volume=22|issue=3/4|pages=343–380|doi=10.18874/jjrs.22.3-4.1995.343-380|jstor=30234459|issn=0304-1042|doi-access=free|access-date=2021-03-27|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227040749/https://www.jstor.org/stable/30234459|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2009年，大川隆法创立幸福实现党并担任党总裁，同年8月宣布参加[[第45届日本众议院议员总选举|第45届日本众议院议员总选举]]，最终落选<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.asahi.com/senkyo2009/news/TKY200908290177.html|title = 大川隆法氏が落選 比例近畿ブロック|accessdate = 2015-12-18|publisher = [[朝日新聞|朝日新聞]]|date = 2009-08-31|archive-date = 2021-05-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210506130303/http://www.asahi.com/senkyo2009/news/TKY200908290177.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2019年3月3日，大川隆法在[[台北|台北]]发表演讲，鼓励[[中华民国与日本关系|日台建交]]，并声称“现在中国是[[霸权|霸权]]、[[极权|极权]]，[[习近平|习近平]]说‘[[一国两制|一国两制]]’，看看香港回归二十多年，已失去自由、民主、快乐和繁荣，北京当局有守信用吗？”<ref>{{cite web|author1=夏小华|author2=陈美华|author3=申铧|author4=瑞哲|url=https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/hx3-03042019095513.html|title=日本幸福科学总裁吁恢复日台建交|work=自由亚洲电台|date=2019-03-04|access-date=2021-04-16|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421154419/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/hx3-03042019095513.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

